In order to validate the home page elements are present 
we will do acceptance testing

steps.name: Navigate to home page "https://www.autotrader.com/" of AutoTrading website
Click on the Advanced Search Button link and page navigate to "Search for Cars For Sale Online - Find a Car at Autotrader"

arguments.val: Search for Cars For Sale Online - Find a Car at Autotrader

steps.name: Enter the ZipCode in text box
Select the Certified Check Box under Condition
Select the Convertible check box under Style
Update the Year drop down menus as follows: select "2017" as From year and select "2020" as To year
Select Make as BMW under Make, Model & Trim section
Page Navigate to "Certified BMW Convertibles for Sale in Alpharetta, GA 30004 - Autotrader" Page
